  <entry>
    <title>Git</title>
    <link href="https://kevinchengchn.github.io/2021/06/03/Git/"/>
    <id>https://kevinchengchn.github.io/2021/06/03/Git/</id>
    <published>2021-06-03T18:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-06-03T18:00:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Git"><a href="#Git" class="headerlink" title="Git"></a>Git</h1><object class="ghbdage" style="margin-inline:5px" title="" standby="loading..." data="https://img.shields.io/badge/git%20branching-learn-orange?logo=&color=254b65&link=https://oschina.gitee.io/learn-git-branching/&"></object><h3 id="将当前修改提交到指定分支"><a href="#将当前修改提交到指定分支" class="headerlink" title="将当前修改提交到指定分支"></a>将当前修改提交到指定分支</h3><blockquote><p>当前在 master 分支，需要将此次修改的代码提交至 dev 分支</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建新分支</span></span><br><span class="line">git branch dev</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将工作区恢复到上次提交的内容，同时备份本地所做的修改</span></span><br><span class="line">git stash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 切换分支</span></span><br><span class="line">git checkout dev</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 从 git 栈中获取到最近一次 stash 的内容，之后会删除栈中对应的 stash</span></span><br><span class="line">git stash pop</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加所有（已修改）文件</span></span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加到本地仓库，Win 注释用双引号</span></span><br><span class="line">git commit <span class="literal">-m</span> <span class="string">&quot;first commit init project&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取</span></span><br><span class="line">git pull origin 远程名称</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 推送</span></span><br><span class="line">git push origin 远程名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="将dev分支的代码合并到master"><a href="#将dev分支的代码合并到master" class="headerlink" title="将dev分支的代码合并到master"></a>将dev分支的代码合并到master</h3><blockquote><p>当前在master分支，需要dev分支的所有代码变动提交至master分支</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 切换到master分支</span></span><br><span class="line">git checkout master</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将dev分支的代码合并到master上</span></span><br><span class="line">git merge dev</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将当前的更改推送到远程的master分支上</span></span><br><span class="line">git push origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="合并某个分支的一个commit到另一个分支"><a href="#合并某个分支的一个commit到另一个分支" class="headerlink" title="合并某个分支的一个commit到另一个分支"></a>合并某个分支的一个commit到另一个分支</h3><blockquote><p>当前在master分支，需要部分代码变动（某几个提交）提交至 dev 分支</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 切换到master分支</span></span><br><span class="line">git checkout master</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取该分支git日志</span></span><br><span class="line">git log</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 找出要合并的commit ID</span></span><br><span class="line">eg：<span class="number">0128660</span>c08e325d410cb845616af355c0c19c6fe</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 切换到dev分支上</span></span><br><span class="line">git checkout dev</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 把master分支的一个或多个commit复制到当前dev分支</span></span><br><span class="line">git cherry<span class="literal">-pick</span> <span class="number">0128660</span>c08e325d410cb845616af355c0c19c6fe</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>git练习：</p>]]></content>
    
    
